title: Urza's Science Fair Project
text: o2: Roll a six-sided die for Urza's Science Fair Project.1 It gets -2/-2 until end of turn.2 It deals no combat damage this turn.3 Attacking does not cause it to tap this turn.4 It gains first strike until end of turn.5 It gains flying until end of turn.6 It gets +2/+2 until end of turn.
